Class ShoppingCart

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.checkout.ShoppingCart

 @SessionScoped
public class ShoppingCart
extends java.lang.Object

    The class ShoppingCart holds the information about the choices user made. It contains shoppingCartLines list for every ticket the user wish to purchase
